ring about 3242394234379097123 different things.  The only way anything will get done is if we agree on One specific thing that needs to be changed.  From what I see there are a number of ways that our problem can be solved.  <br>
<br>
A&gt; Increase Dmg on Wiz spells<br>
B&gt; Lower mana costs<br>
C&gt; Make equipment that can increas DMG output or lower mana cost<br>
<br>
I don't know if this will completely solve all of our problems, but I think that it is what we are all trying to get done.  Ideally all 3 should be put into the came at certain degrees.  Again im not saying to make wizards &quot;uber&quot; just to make us useful.  Hopefully we can use this thread to try to get one basic idea that we would like verant to change, and not just &quot;fix wizards&quot;.  After that maybe all of us can drill it into them as much as we can till they do something……   What have we got to loose ?<br>
